    "We then matched the transcripts and engagement data using the talk titles.",
    "Entries were matched using two strategies.",
    "First, we identified 2475 exact title matches.",
    "Then, we looked for matches in the remaining 1070 using approximate string matching and manual checking.",
    "This was necessary because many talks are published on YouTube using a different title than is used on the TED website."
